BRIEF-Crown Resorts Reaches Agreement With ATO To Settle Dispute

Stock Markets 21 minutes ago (Oct 17, 2019 19:56)

© Reuters. BRIEF-Crown Resorts Reaches Agreement With ATO To Settle Dispute Oct 17 (Reuters) - Crown Resorts Ltd : * REACHED AGREEMENT WITH ATO TO SETTLE DISPUTE & RELATED ISSUES ARISING IN RESPECT OF FINANCIAL YEARS ENDED 30 JUNE 2015 TO 30 JUNE 2018 * SETTLEMENT DOES NOT RESULT IN MATERIAL IMPACTS TO CROWN'S CURRENT OR FUTURE YEAR FINANCIAL RESULTS * TERMS OF SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT ARE CONFIDENTIAL
